&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OTE range for this role is $150,000 - $300,000 (Base + Bonus)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary and performance-based bonuses&lt;/li&gt;
